      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PAW BRUTUS (5) finished in the placings last time but could not have been more impressive three back in his powerful 29.96 win at this track over 525m. Hard to top on best recent times. HAPPY DAD (2) has been hard to follow lately, running fifth (30.58) last time but prior to that ran very well when placed at this track. This looks easier and expected to improve sharply. ASTON HERCULES (8) was below best latest but did hit the frame in quick time two back when third (27.41) at Horsham in a Grade 4/5. Can turn it around this time. JILL'S FANTASY (1) cannot be left out despite racing here for the first time.",
